00:35:55,840 --> 00:35:57,000
possesses poetic talent,

579
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:58,880
is skilled in calligraphy and dance,

580
00:35:59,120 --> 00:36:00,360
good in scholarship,

581
00:36:00,680 --> 00:36:01,800
knowledgeable,

582
00:36:02,720 --> 00:36:04,440
known for her virtue and grace,

583
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:06,160
and her reputation unparalleled in Xiang'an.

584
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:08,720
Which of these descriptions

585
00:36:10,320 --> 00:36:11,720
fits you?

