00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:43,280
If you don't want to end up with

603
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,640
a broken leg or

604
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,840
a missing arm here at the Shen residence,

605
00:37:49,120 --> 00:37:50,720
