00:38:22,560 --> 00:38:23,400
My lord,

608
00:38:24,880 --> 00:38:26,600
since Her Highness had said so,

609
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:28,240
then I'll fulfill my responsibilities

610
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:30,440
as the Lady of the Shen residence

611
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,440
and take really good care

612
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:35,000
of you.

613
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:41,360
This is how you

614
00:38:42,280 --> 00:38:43,800
