615
00:39:24,600 --> 00:39:26,480
Since you said you would take care of me,

616
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:29,360
then let me tell you three things.

617
00:39:31,960 --> 00:39:32,760
First,

618
00:39:34,240 --> 00:39:35,240
don't even dream about

619
00:39:35,240 --> 00:39:36,680
becoming the real Lady Shen.

620
00:39:37,440 --> 00:39:38,600
It's only an act

621
00:39:39,200 --> 00:39:40,400
between us.

622
00:39:41,440 --> 00:39:42,240
Second,

623
00:39:43,440 --> 00:39:44,680
don't expect to get any

624
00:39:44,680 --> 00:39:46,040
information from me.

625
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:48,920
I know what Prime Minister Zhang

626
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:50,080
sent you here for.

627
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:54,880
Third,

628
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:57,360
you're not the wife

629
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:59,320
that I willingly chose.

630
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:02,360
Don't even think about surviving here.

631
00:40:51,480 --> 00:40:52,280
Lord,

632
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,720
did you see Lady Shen?

633
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:57,680
And the wedding ceremony...

634
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:58,960
Just think of it as if it's done.

635
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:00,280
Then,

636
00:41:00,560 --> 00:41:01,760
about the West Chamber...

637
00:41:08,200 --> 00:41:09,520
Let her stay there.

